      <h1 class="title">
      Discutir o presente e o futuro da rede: I Fórum da Internet no Brasil
  </h1>
  <span class="publishing-info">
  <span class="date">
    Ottobre 12, 2011 0:00
  </span>
  <span class="author">
    , by Software Livre Brasil
  </span>
  <span class="comments">
     - <a href="/colivre/blog/discutir-o-presente-e-o-futuro-da-rede-i-forum-da-internet-no-brasil#comments_list"><span class='comment-count hide'>0</span><span class='comment-count-write-out'>no comments yet</span></a>
